ProtectiveFactorCodeSearchParameter D

Parameter workflow-protectiveFactorCode:token

SearchParameter for Protective Factor Extension with CodeableConcept data type

ResourcesCarePlan, CommunicationRequest, Goal
ExpressionCarePlan.activity.extension('http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/workflow-protectiveFactor').value.concept | CommunicationRequest.extension('http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/workflow-protectiveFactor').value.concept | Goal.extension('http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/workflow-protectiveFactor').value.concept
Processing ModeNormal
Multiples
  • multipleAnd: It's up to the server whether the parameter may repeat in order to specify multiple values that must all be true
  • multipleOr: It's up to the server whether the parameter can have multiple values (separated by comma) where at least one must be true
